<emphasis bold="true" box="[875,1029,1083,1106]" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">Figures 1–2:</emphasis>
Chela of pedipalp showing external trichobothria. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1019,1038,1110,1131]" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">1.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authority="(Birula, 1900)" baseAuthorityName="Birula" baseAuthorityYear="1900" box="[1051,1436,1110,1131]" class="Arachnida" family="Buthidae" genus="Sassanidotus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scorpiones" pageId="3" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zarudnyi">
<emphasis box="[1051,1275,1110,1131]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">Sassanidotus zarudnyi</emphasis>
(Birula, 1900)
</taxonomicName>
, male neotype. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1031,1049,1134,1155]" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">2.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authority="(Birula, 1900)" baseAuthorityName="Birula" baseAuthorityYear="1900" box="[1063,1434,1134,1155]" class="Arachnida" family="Buthidae" genus="Sassanidotus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scorpiones" pageId="3" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gracilis">
<emphasis box="[1063,1277,1134,1155]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">Sassanidotus gracilis</emphasis>
(Birula, 1900)
</taxonomicName>
, female holotype.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph blockId="3.[192,802,1218,1916]" lastBlockId="3.[830,1441,1218,1916]" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">
Vachon, however, never published a new generic name for 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Birula" authorityYear="1900" box="[309,490,1586,1609]" class="Arachnida" family="Buthidae" genus="Buthus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scorpiones" pageId="3" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zarudnyi">
<emphasis box="[309,490,1586,1609]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">Buthus zarudnyi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Farzanpay (1988: 39, 40) listed the name (spelled with “th” as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Farzanpay" authorityYear="1988" box="[642,795,1617,1640]" class="Arachnida" family="Buthidae" genus="Sassanidothus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scorpiones" pageId="3" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[642,795,1617,1640]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">Sassanidothus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, which constitutes an incorrect subsequent spelling) along with two other new scorpion genera, where he planned to be one of the authors: “ 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Farzanpay" authorityYear="1987" box="[579,678,1709,1732]" class="Arachnida" family="Buthidae" genus="Olivierus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scorpiones" pageId="3" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[579,678,1709,1732]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">Olivierus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(n. gen. to be described by Farzanpay &amp; Vachon),” “ 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Farzanpay" authorityYear="1987" box="[664,762,1739,1762]" class="Arachnida" family="Buthidae" genus="Razianus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scorpiones" pageId="3" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[664,762,1739,1762]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">Razianus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(n. gen. to be described by Vachon &amp; Farzanpay),” and “ 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Farzanpay" authorityYear="1988" box="[204,357,1801,1824]" class="Arachnida" family="Buthidae" genus="Sassanidothus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scorpiones" pageId="3" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[204,357,1801,1824]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">Sassanidothus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(n. gen. to be described by Farzanpay &amp; Vachon)”. In the introduction, he wrote (Farzanpay, 1988: 34): “The new creations are based on the cooperation and suggestion of Professor Max Vachon of the Muséum national d´Histoire naturelle in Paris as agreed by personal communication. ...(letter 
<date pageId="3" pageNumber="2" value="1984-08-30">August 30, 1984</date>
)”.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[830,1441,1218,1916]" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">
Unfortunately, no further descriptions of these genera by Vachon ever appeared until Vachon’s death in 1992; there is also no evidence that Vachon was aware that descriptions of three new genera and one new species were published by Farzanpay (1987). About 
<specimenCount pageId="3" pageNumber="2" type="generic">20 specimens</specimenCount>
from 
<collectingCountry box="[1007,1050,1463,1486]" name="Iran" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">Iran</collectingCountry>
labeled “ 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Farzanpay" authorityYear="1988" box="[1152,1305,1463,1486]" class="Arachnida" family="Buthidae" genus="Sassanidothus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scorpiones" pageId="3" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1152,1305,1463,1486]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">Sassanidothus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
” by 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03D187ABFFD9FFB4962BF9AAFAE3F8A0:8EA76066FFD8FFB4922BFA60FA35FA12" box="[1357,1440,1463,1486]" country="Iran" name="Vachon" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">Vachon</location>
exist in 
<collectionCode box="[920,1001,1494,1517]" country="France" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34988" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34988" name="Museum National d'Histoire Naturelle" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">MNHN</collectionCode>
(pers. comm. from 
<collectorName box="[1222,1410,1494,1517]" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">Wilson Lourenço</collectorName>
to 
<collectorName box="[830,877,1525,1548]" name="Victor Fet" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">V.F.</collectorName>
, 1996).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[830,1441,1218,1916]" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">
The genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Farzanpay" authorityYear="1987" box="[1014,1153,1555,1578]" class="Arachnida" family="Buthidae" genus="Sassanidotus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scorpiones" pageId="3" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1014,1153,1555,1578]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">Sassanidotus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was never revised, and therefore was considered valid by Fet &amp; Lowe (2000: 222), as well as other genera published in Farzanpay (1987), namely, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Farzanpay" authorityYear="1987" box="[1020,1119,1647,1670]" class="Arachnida" family="Buthidae" genus="Olivierus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scorpiones" pageId="3" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1020,1119,1647,1670]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">Olivierus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Farzanpay" authorityYear="1987" box="[1140,1238,1647,1670]" class="Arachnida" family="Buthidae" genus="Razianus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scorpiones" pageId="3" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1140,1238,1647,1670]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">Razianus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName box="[1310,1433,1647,1670]" class="Arachnida" family="Buthidae" genus="Simonoides" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scorpiones" pageId="3" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1310,1433,1647,1670]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">Simonoides</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. The authorship of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Farzanpay" authorityYear="1987" box="[1117,1216,1678,1701]" class="Arachnida" family="Buthidae" genus="Olivierus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scorpiones" pageId="3" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1117,1216,1678,1701]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">Olivierus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Farzanpay" authorityYear="1987" box="[1260,1358,1678,1701]" class="Arachnida" family="Buthidae" genus="Razianus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scorpiones" pageId="3" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1260,1358,1678,1701]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">Razianus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Farzanpay" authorityYear="1987" box="[830,969,1709,1732]" class="Arachnida" family="Buthidae" genus="Sassanidotus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scorpiones" pageId="3" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[830,969,1709,1732]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">Sassanidotus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, however, was assigned only to Farzanpay (1987) by Fet &amp; Lowe (2000: 189, 216, 222) since they did not think that Vachon was responsible for the descriptions (quite incomplete and inadequate) as published by Farzanpay (1987). On complicated authorship of 
<taxonomicName box="[991,1114,1862,1885]" class="Arachnida" family="Buthidae" genus="Simonoides" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scorpiones" pageId="3" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[991,1114,1862,1885]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">Simonoides</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(now confirmed as a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Karsch" authorityYear="1892" box="[964,1094,1893,1916]" class="Arachnida" family="Buthidae" genus="Orthochirus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scorpiones" pageId="3" pageNumber="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[964,1094,1893,1916]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="2">Orthochirus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), see Kovařík &amp; Fet (2006).
</paragraph>
